11
00:03:35,960 --> 00:03:37,759
[SPEAKER_02] i voditeljice emisije

12
00:03:37,759 --> 00:03:39,159
[SPEAKER_02] Franjina Ekonomija.

13
00:03:39,159 --> 00:03:41,860
[SPEAKER_02] Tehnički urednik danas na nje je gospodin

14
00:03:41,860 --> 00:03:43,680
[SPEAKER_02] Ivan Zaradić. Evo nas,

15
00:03:43,680 --> 00:03:45,659
[SPEAKER_02] posljedetne stanke, otvaramo

16
00:03:45,659 --> 00:03:47,939
[SPEAKER_02] novi ciklus unutar naše emisije.

17
00:03:47,939 --> 00:03:49,740
[SPEAKER_02] U sljedećim

18
00:03:49,740 --> 00:03:51,860
[SPEAKER_02] mjesecima govorit ćemo o tematskoj

19
00:03:51,860 --> 00:03:53,240
[SPEAKER_02] cijelini poziv i profit.

20
00:03:53,240 --> 00:03:55,300
[SPEAKER_02] Tema će nam biti školstvo,

21
00:03:55,300 --> 00:03:57,080
[SPEAKER_02] obrazovanje kao poziv.

22
00:03:57,080 --> 00:03:59,620
[SPEAKER_02] U odnosu na profit,

23
00:03:59,620 --> 00:04:01,300
[SPEAKER_02] koja je ekonomska vrijednost,

24
00:04:01,300 --> 00:04:03,879
[SPEAKER_02] rekli smo na samim početcima ove emisije

25
00:04:03,879 --> 00:04:06,000
[SPEAKER_02] da profit se ne odnose

26
00:04:06,000 --> 00:04:08,000
[SPEAKER_02] samo na ručunovodstveni profit,

27
00:04:08,000 --> 00:04:10,180
[SPEAKER_02] već da je ekonomija i znanost.

28
00:04:10,180 --> 00:04:11,900
[SPEAKER_02] I to društvena znanost

29
00:04:11,900 --> 00:04:14,120
[SPEAKER_02] koja se bavi proučavanjem društva

30
00:04:14,120 --> 00:04:15,639
[SPEAKER_02] kako društva

31
00:04:15,639 --> 00:04:17,699
[SPEAKER_02] upotrebljavaju oskudne resurse

32
00:04:17,699 --> 00:04:19,579
[SPEAKER_02] da bi proizvela određena

33
00:04:19,579 --> 00:04:21,259
[SPEAKER_02] dobra i usluge

34
00:04:21,259 --> 00:04:23,079
[SPEAKER_02] i raspodijela ih među njima.

35
00:04:23,079 --> 00:04:25,079
[SPEAKER_02] Rekli smo da je ekonomija

36
00:04:25,079 --> 00:04:27,600
[SPEAKER_02] dolazi od grčke riječi oikonomija

37
00:04:27,600 --> 00:04:29,579
[SPEAKER_02] što znači oikos

38
00:04:29,579 --> 00:04:30,959
[SPEAKER_02] i nomos

39
00:04:30,959 --> 00:04:33,339
[SPEAKER_02] što znači zakon, upravljati,

40
00:04:33,339 --> 00:04:35,439
[SPEAKER_02] a oikos što znači kuća,

41
00:04:35,439 --> 00:04:38,839
[SPEAKER_02] odnosno gospodarstvo, obitelj, imovina.

42
00:04:38,839 --> 00:04:41,759
[SPEAKER_02] I tako imamo upravljanje imovinom,

43
00:04:41,759 --> 00:04:43,459
[SPEAKER_02] upravljanje obitelj,

44
00:04:43,459 --> 00:04:45,000
[SPEAKER_02] upravljanje gospodarstvom,

45
00:04:45,000 --> 00:04:46,720
[SPEAKER_02] upravljanje i školstvom.

46
00:04:47,759 --> 00:04:49,699
[SPEAKER_02] Obitelj nam je, rekli smo,

47
00:04:49,699 --> 00:04:51,600
[SPEAKER_02] temeljna društvena zajednica.

48
00:04:51,600 --> 00:04:53,720
[SPEAKER_02] Evo, temeljna društvena zajednica,

49
00:04:53,720 --> 00:04:54,759
[SPEAKER_02] muškarca i žene.

50
00:04:54,759 --> 00:04:57,740
[SPEAKER_02] I danas ćemo pričat, znači,

51
00:04:57,740 --> 00:05:00,779
[SPEAKER_02] o školstvu gdje mi stavljamo

52
00:05:00,779 --> 00:05:01,639
[SPEAKER_02] našu djecu

53
00:05:01,639 --> 00:05:04,560
[SPEAKER_02] i kako ta djeca, kako te generacije

54
00:05:04,560 --> 00:05:06,339
[SPEAKER_02] onda dalje stvaraju

55
00:05:06,339 --> 00:05:09,139
[SPEAKER_02] i donose nove generacije.

56
00:05:09,139 --> 00:05:10,120
[SPEAKER_02] S nama je gost,

57
00:05:10,120 --> 00:05:12,639
[SPEAKER_02] gospodin profesor Dejan Nemčić.

58
00:05:12,639 --> 00:05:14,000
[SPEAKER_02] Dejan, je dobro dan došao.

59
00:05:14,339 --> 00:05:17,079
[SPEAKER_00] Dobar dan, evo, hvala na lijepom dočeku

60
00:05:17,079 --> 00:05:18,660
[SPEAKER_00] i hvala na lijepim riječima

61
00:05:18,660 --> 00:05:20,779
[SPEAKER_00] i evo, i dobar dan svim slušateljima.

62
00:05:20,779 --> 00:05:23,420
[SPEAKER_02] Dejan je profesor geografije,

63
00:05:23,420 --> 00:05:25,360
[SPEAKER_02] predaje u osnovnoj školi,

64
00:05:25,360 --> 00:05:27,120
[SPEAKER_02] je li tako, Ivo Andrić.

65
00:05:27,120 --> 00:05:28,779
[SPEAKER_02] On je, evo Dejan,

66
00:05:28,779 --> 00:05:29,800
[SPEAKER_02] ne možeš nam malo i ti reći,

67
00:05:29,800 --> 00:05:31,839
[SPEAKER_02] da ne pričam ja o tebi,

68
00:05:31,839 --> 00:05:32,420
[SPEAKER_02] reći nam ti.

69
00:05:32,420 --> 00:05:34,360
[SPEAKER_00] Najteže je sebe predstaviti nekako,

70
00:05:34,360 --> 00:05:36,639
[SPEAKER_00] ali evo, kad smo u takoj emisiji,

71
00:05:36,639 --> 00:05:38,500
[SPEAKER_00] ovoga, nekako ćemo biti

72
00:05:38,500 --> 00:05:40,819
[SPEAKER_00] točni onako, kad predajemo

73
00:05:40,819 --> 00:05:41,420
[SPEAKER_00] u osnovnoj školi,

74
00:05:41,420 --> 00:05:42,300
[SPEAKER_00] da smo učitelji,

75
00:05:42,360 --> 00:05:44,240
[SPEAKER_00] mislim da nema ništa ljepše riječi

76
00:05:44,240 --> 00:05:45,639
[SPEAKER_00] od učitelj nekako

77
00:05:45,639 --> 00:05:47,639
[SPEAKER_00] i da predajem i u srednjoj školi

78
00:05:47,639 --> 00:05:48,399
[SPEAKER_00] i na fakultetu,

79
00:05:48,399 --> 00:05:50,019
[SPEAKER_00] voli bi biti učitelj ovoga.

80
00:05:50,019 --> 00:05:52,459
[SPEAKER_00] Tako da, najljepša riječ je učitelj,

81
00:05:52,459 --> 00:05:55,300
[SPEAKER_00] ali evo, učitelj geografije,

82
00:05:55,300 --> 00:05:58,399
[SPEAKER_00] dosta se bavim i humanitarnim radom,

83
00:05:58,399 --> 00:06:00,180
[SPEAKER_00] dosta radim na edukaciji,

84
00:06:00,180 --> 00:06:02,060
[SPEAKER_00] ne samo u nastavi geografije

85
00:06:02,060 --> 00:06:02,959
[SPEAKER_00] u svojoj školi,

86
00:06:02,959 --> 00:06:04,980
[SPEAKER_00] ali prije svega želim

87
00:06:04,980 --> 00:06:06,319
[SPEAKER_00] kroz svoje radnje vije,

88
00:06:06,319 --> 00:06:08,379
[SPEAKER_00] kroz svoje svakodnevno djelovanje

89
00:06:08,379 --> 00:06:10,879
[SPEAKER_00] promijeniti percepciju škole,

90
00:06:10,959 --> 00:06:12,980
[SPEAKER_00] a to je da djeca dolaze sa osmijehom,

91
00:06:12,980 --> 00:06:16,000
[SPEAKER_00] a da odlaze doma sa još jednim većim osmijehom.

92
00:06:16,000 --> 00:06:17,639
[SPEAKER_00] Tako da sam se dao ovako jednu

93
00:06:17,639 --> 00:06:19,779
[SPEAKER_00] životnu priliku,

94
00:06:19,779 --> 00:06:21,360
[SPEAKER_00] kao učitelj geografije,

95
00:06:21,360 --> 00:06:22,699
[SPEAKER_00] da to mijenjam

96
00:06:22,699 --> 00:06:24,519
[SPEAKER_00] i mislim da smo na dobrom putu

97
00:06:24,519 --> 00:06:25,420
[SPEAKER_00] da i to napravimo.

98
00:06:26,120 --> 00:06:27,660
[SPEAKER_02] Odlično, evo, učitelj,

99
00:06:27,660 --> 00:06:28,819
[SPEAKER_02] ja bih rekla učitelj,

100
00:06:28,819 --> 00:06:30,899
[SPEAKER_02] dolaze od riječi znači učiti,

101
00:06:30,899 --> 00:06:32,560
[SPEAKER_02] učiti nekoga, ne?

102
00:06:32,560 --> 00:06:33,980
[SPEAKER_02] Pa, dobro je,

103
00:06:33,980 --> 00:06:35,579
[SPEAKER_02] onda učitelj,

104
00:06:35,579 --> 00:06:37,459
[SPEAKER_02] poziv ili posao?

105
00:06:37,459 --> 00:06:38,839
[SPEAKER_02] Evo, da odmah direktno ovaj,

106
00:06:38,839 --> 00:06:39,480
[SPEAKER_02] pređemo na to.

107
00:06:39,480 --> 00:06:41,079
[SPEAKER_00] Toliko sam već konferencija

108
00:06:41,079 --> 00:06:43,019
[SPEAKER_00] i gostovanja po medijima bio

109
00:06:43,019 --> 00:06:44,459
[SPEAKER_00] i uvijek je to vječno pitanje,

110
00:06:44,459 --> 00:06:46,660
[SPEAKER_00] da li je to poziv ili to je posao,

111
00:06:46,759 --> 00:06:47,980
[SPEAKER_00] ali uvijek se volim šaliti

112
00:06:47,980 --> 00:06:49,500
[SPEAKER_00] ovoga učitelj kad spomenete,

113
00:06:49,500 --> 00:06:50,660
[SPEAKER_00] onda mi uvijek u mislima

114
00:06:50,660 --> 00:06:51,920
[SPEAKER_00] kad krenu ispiti,

115
00:06:51,920 --> 00:06:52,959
[SPEAKER_00] onda je mučitelj,

116
00:06:52,959 --> 00:06:54,060
[SPEAKER_00] nije više učitelj,

117
00:06:54,060 --> 00:06:55,920
[SPEAKER_00] tako da je mučitelj djeca ovoga,

118
00:06:55,920 --> 00:06:57,160
[SPEAKER_00] ovoga nekako,

119
00:06:57,160 --> 00:06:59,339
[SPEAKER_00] djeca uvijek misli da mi njih mučimo,

120
00:06:59,339 --> 00:07:00,519
[SPEAKER_00] znači mi njih ne mučimo,

121
00:07:00,519 --> 00:07:02,620
[SPEAKER_00] mi moramo mijenjati tu sliku obrazovanja,

122
00:07:02,620 --> 00:07:04,720
[SPEAKER_00] da mi jednostavno njih pripremamo za život.

123
00:07:04,720 --> 00:07:06,319
[SPEAKER_00] I to mislim da se izgubilo

124
00:07:06,319 --> 00:07:07,720
[SPEAKER_00] nekako u školama,

125
00:07:07,720 --> 00:07:09,879
[SPEAKER_00] taj osjećaj zašto mi idemo u školu,

126
00:07:09,879 --> 00:07:11,259
[SPEAKER_00] zašto djeca idu u školu.

127
00:07:11,660 --> 00:07:12,639
[SPEAKER_00] Da li je to poziv,

128
00:07:12,639 --> 00:07:13,959
[SPEAKER_00] da li je to posao?

129
00:07:13,959 --> 00:07:15,959
[SPEAKER_00] Ja ne mogu govoriti

130
00:07:15,959 --> 00:07:17,259
[SPEAKER_00] o ime svih učitelja,

131
00:07:17,259 --> 00:07:20,279
[SPEAKER_00] koliko nas ima možda 50 tisuća u Hrvatskoj,

132
00:07:20,279 --> 00:07:22,199
[SPEAKER_00] ali ja gledam iz svoje perspektive,

133
00:07:22,199 --> 00:07:23,600
[SPEAKER_00] ja to gledam kao poziv.

134
00:07:23,600 --> 00:07:26,779
[SPEAKER_00] Budući da sam ja svoje radno vrijeme

135
00:07:26,779 --> 00:07:28,240
[SPEAKER_00] danas završio jedan sat,

136
00:07:28,240 --> 00:07:30,360
[SPEAKER_00] ja sam sada evo tu uživo u vašoj emisiji,

137
00:07:30,360 --> 00:07:31,740
[SPEAKER_00] ovo je moje slobodno vrijeme.

138
00:07:31,740 --> 00:07:34,680
[SPEAKER_00] I ja nekako isto ulazim tu u ovu emisiju

139
00:07:34,680 --> 00:07:36,879
[SPEAKER_00] kao iz uloge učitelja

140
00:07:36,879 --> 00:07:38,800
[SPEAKER_00] i onda nekako gledaš

141
00:07:38,800 --> 00:07:40,139
[SPEAKER_00] da nije to samo posao.

142
00:07:40,459 --> 00:07:42,519
[SPEAKER_00] Ja to doživljam stvarno kao poziv

143
00:07:42,519 --> 00:07:45,540
[SPEAKER_00] i nekako se osjećam počašćeno

144
00:07:45,540 --> 00:07:48,040
[SPEAKER_00] i privilegirano da mogu raditi taj posao.

145
00:07:48,040 --> 00:07:50,459
[SPEAKER_00] I naravno, danas imate učitelje

146
00:07:50,459 --> 00:07:51,939
[SPEAKER_00] koji to tako doživljavaju,

147
00:07:51,939 --> 00:07:53,920
[SPEAKER_00] koji stvarno uživaju i smatraju

148
00:07:53,920 --> 00:07:56,199
[SPEAKER_00] da im je to važna uloga u društvu

149
00:07:56,199 --> 00:07:57,079
[SPEAKER_00] biti učitelj,

150
00:07:57,079 --> 00:07:59,920
[SPEAKER_00] a imate učitelje koji idu u ovaj posao

151
00:07:59,920 --> 00:08:01,220
[SPEAKER_00] je ono što se uvijek vrti,

152
00:08:01,220 --> 00:08:02,779
[SPEAKER_00] tri mjeseca praznika,

153
00:08:02,779 --> 00:08:05,040
[SPEAKER_00] radiš do 12 sati,

154
00:08:05,040 --> 00:08:07,240
[SPEAKER_00] imaš slobodno puno vremena,

155
00:08:07,240 --> 00:08:09,259
[SPEAKER_00] ali učitelj koji je svim srcem

156
00:08:09,259 --> 00:08:10,560
[SPEAKER_00] u svom razredu,

157
00:08:10,560 --> 00:08:12,560
[SPEAKER_00] koji se stvarno trudi od tih mladih

158
00:08:12,560 --> 00:08:14,459
[SPEAKER_00] napraviti male, velike ljude,

159
00:08:14,459 --> 00:08:16,779
[SPEAKER_00] ja mislim da on ima radno vrijeme.

160
00:08:16,779 --> 00:08:18,060
[SPEAKER_00] Jer ja vidim i po sebi.

161
00:08:18,060 --> 00:08:20,560
[SPEAKER_00] Ja ne znam kad sam otišao doma,

162
00:08:20,560 --> 00:08:21,779
[SPEAKER_00] kad mi je nastava završila.

163
00:08:21,779 --> 00:08:23,240
[SPEAKER_00] To se uvijek nešto priprema,

164
00:08:23,240 --> 00:08:24,920
[SPEAKER_00] puno se razgovara sa mladima

165
00:08:24,920 --> 00:08:30,379
[SPEAKER_00] i mislim da kao učitelj imam veliku odgovornost prema njima.

166
00:08:30,379 --> 00:08:32,159
[SPEAKER_00] jer mladi su nam danas izgubljeni.

167
00:08:32,159 --> 00:08:34,179
[SPEAKER_00] Oni ako nemaju potporu,

168
00:08:34,179 --> 00:08:35,100
[SPEAKER_00] barem škole,

169
00:08:35,100 --> 00:08:36,679
[SPEAKER_00] u ovom ludom svijetu,

170
00:08:36,679 --> 00:08:37,519
[SPEAKER_00] brzog tempa,

171
00:08:37,519 --> 00:08:39,480
[SPEAKER_00] gdje roditelji jure za karijerom,

172
00:08:39,480 --> 00:08:39,759
[SPEAKER_00] za egzistencijom,

173
00:08:39,759 --> 00:08:42,080
[SPEAKER_00] ako i mi, učitelji,

174
00:08:42,080 --> 00:08:43,360
[SPEAKER_00] još okrenemo leđa,

175
00:08:43,360 --> 00:08:45,019
[SPEAKER_00] onda se nemamo čuditi

176
00:08:45,019 --> 00:08:46,580
[SPEAKER_00] kad se događaju loše stvari

177
00:08:46,580 --> 00:08:47,519
[SPEAKER_00] s našim mladima

178
00:08:47,519 --> 00:08:49,960
[SPEAKER_00] i kad slušamo crnu kroniku mlade u crnoj kronici.

179
00:08:49,960 --> 00:08:51,639
[SPEAKER_00] Tako da,

180
00:08:51,639 --> 00:08:53,460
[SPEAKER_00] evo, ako i mladi učitelji

181
00:08:53,460 --> 00:08:55,419
[SPEAKER_00] sada slušaju ovaj intervju,

182
00:08:55,419 --> 00:08:57,399
[SPEAKER_00] imate prevažnu ulogu

183
00:08:57,399 --> 00:08:59,120
[SPEAKER_00] i nikada nemojte dopustiti

184
00:08:59,120 --> 00:09:00,419
[SPEAKER_00] da vam se dijete obrati,

185
00:09:00,419 --> 00:09:01,559
[SPEAKER_00] a da vi okrenete

186
00:09:01,559 --> 00:09:03,519
[SPEAKER_00] i da vam bude kava sa prijateljicom

187
00:09:03,519 --> 00:09:04,799
[SPEAKER_00] ili prijateljem važnija

188
00:09:04,799 --> 00:09:06,480
[SPEAKER_00] od razgovora sa učenikom.

189
00:09:06,480 --> 00:09:09,899
[SPEAKER_00] Jedna rečenica koja mene uvijek vodi u mom radu,

190
00:09:09,899 --> 00:09:13,019
[SPEAKER_00] bolje je jedan izgubljeni sad geografije

191
00:09:13,019 --> 00:09:14,480
[SPEAKER_00] nego jedan izgubljeni život.

192
00:09:14,480 --> 00:09:16,580
[SPEAKER_00] I to je ono što me svake put

193
00:09:16,580 --> 00:09:17,960
[SPEAKER_00] kad pređem prak škole

194
00:09:17,960 --> 00:09:19,019
[SPEAKER_00] vodi u mom radu.

195
00:09:19,960 --> 00:09:21,240
[SPEAKER_02] Odlično.

196
00:09:21,240 --> 00:09:22,360
[SPEAKER_02] Jako lijepo.

197
00:09:22,360 --> 00:09:23,580
[SPEAKER_02] Ja bih rekla da je u biti

198
00:09:23,580 --> 00:09:25,519
[SPEAKER_02] onda i osobna odgovornost

199
00:09:25,519 --> 00:09:27,320
[SPEAKER_02] svakog od nas

200
00:09:27,320 --> 00:09:28,980
[SPEAKER_02] da li prihvaća svoj poziv,

201
00:09:28,980 --> 00:09:30,940
[SPEAKER_02] svoj posao kao poziv

202
00:09:30,940 --> 00:09:33,419
[SPEAKER_02] ili kao nešto još što će

203
00:09:33,419 --> 00:09:35,039
[SPEAKER_02] odraditi 8 sati

204
00:09:35,039 --> 00:09:37,500
