[SPEAKER_02] I tko će odgajati našu djecu?

1794
00:55:39,199 --> 00:55:41,099
[SPEAKER_00] E, ovo je pitanje budućnosti,

1795
00:55:41,099 --> 00:55:42,880
[SPEAKER_00] sjetiti će se vi ovi koji ste slušali,

1796
00:55:42,880 --> 00:55:43,579
[SPEAKER_00] evo, i riječ mi je,

1797
00:55:43,579 --> 00:55:45,500
[SPEAKER_00] progutao sam koliko sam se uznamirio odmah.

1798
00:55:45,500 --> 00:55:46,619
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, malo razmišljamo,

1799
00:55:46,619 --> 00:55:47,500
[SPEAKER_00] malo razmišljamo,

1800
00:55:47,500 --> 00:55:49,900
[SPEAKER_02] malo razmišljamo do tome,

1801
00:55:50,000 --> 00:55:52,760
[SPEAKER_02] sljedeći put ćemo pričati isto,

1802
00:55:52,760 --> 00:55:56,599
[SPEAKER_02] Jane, o humanitarnom radu.

1803
00:55:56,599 --> 00:55:59,619
[SPEAKER_02] Kako Afrika može pomoći hrvatskoj djeci?

1804
00:55:59,619 --> 00:56:00,659
[SPEAKER_00] U, jako puno.

1805
00:56:00,659 --> 00:56:01,300
[SPEAKER_00] Kako može?

1806
00:56:01,300 --> 00:56:02,860
[SPEAKER_00] Mnoga djeca su se promijenila

1807
00:56:02,860 --> 00:56:04,039
[SPEAKER_00] ovih pet godina

1808
00:56:04,039 --> 00:56:05,139
[SPEAKER_00] od kad odlazimo u Afriku,

1809
00:56:05,139 --> 00:56:06,699
[SPEAKER_00] da su shvatili toliko

1810
00:56:06,699 --> 00:56:08,079
[SPEAKER_00] koliko je njihov život lijep,

1811
00:56:08,079 --> 00:56:09,079
[SPEAKER_00] a to je najveća nagrada.

1812
00:56:09,079 --> 00:56:11,340
[SPEAKER_00] Koliko nam je Afrika dala ljudi?

1813
00:56:11,340 --> 00:56:12,300
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, zadaća isto

1814
00:56:12,300 --> 00:56:13,800
[SPEAKER_00] koji nas sada slušaju,

1815
00:56:13,800 --> 00:56:15,219
[SPEAKER_00] koji će nas sljedeći put slušati.

1816
00:56:15,219 --> 00:56:16,440
[SPEAKER_00] Afrika nije kontinent,

1817
00:56:16,440 --> 00:56:17,099
[SPEAKER_00] samo Afrika.

1818
00:56:17,099 --> 00:56:18,119
[SPEAKER_00] Afrika je bakica

1819
00:56:18,119 --> 00:56:20,500
[SPEAKER_00] koja ima 300 eura mirovine,

1820
00:56:20,500 --> 00:56:22,219
[SPEAKER_00] ona bakica koja ne može sići

1821
00:56:22,219 --> 00:56:24,659
[SPEAKER_00] dolje do trgovine

1822
00:56:24,659 --> 00:56:25,960
[SPEAKER_00] koji bi trebali pomoći

1823
00:56:25,960 --> 00:56:28,099
[SPEAKER_00] i ona bakica koja padne na ulici

1824
00:56:28,099 --> 00:56:30,880
[SPEAKER_00] i onaj beskućnik koji leži na klupi

1825
00:56:30,880 --> 00:56:32,079
[SPEAKER_00] i danas treba nešto pojesti.

1826
00:56:32,079 --> 00:56:33,599
[SPEAKER_00] Znači Afrika je među nama.

1827
00:56:33,599 --> 00:56:34,760
[SPEAKER_00] Afrika je u nama,

1828
00:56:34,760 --> 00:56:36,219
[SPEAKER_00] među nama i pored nas.

1829
00:56:36,219 --> 00:56:37,480
[SPEAKER_00] Tako da ćemo o tome pričati.

1830
00:56:39,079 --> 00:56:40,079
[SPEAKER_02] Gledatelji, dragi gledatelji,

1831
00:56:40,079 --> 00:56:40,880
[SPEAKER_02] bilo mi je drago,

1832
00:56:40,880 --> 00:56:41,840
[SPEAKER_02] jako mi je bila čast.

1833
00:56:41,840 --> 00:56:42,480
[SPEAKER_02] Evo, Dejana,

1834
00:56:42,480 --> 00:56:45,300
[SPEAKER_02] ugosti tu našu emisiju.

1835
00:56:45,300 --> 00:56:46,860
[SPEAKER_02] Dejane, hvala ti još jedan put.

1836
00:56:46,860 --> 00:56:47,179
[SPEAKER_02] Hvala vama.

1837
00:56:47,179 --> 00:56:49,400
[SPEAKER_02] Vidimo se za mjesec dana.

1838
00:56:49,400 --> 00:56:51,320
[SPEAKER_02] Moje ime je Katarina Bukša,

1839
00:56:51,320 --> 00:56:53,480
[SPEAKER_02] ja sam urednica i voditeljica

1840
00:56:53,480 --> 00:56:55,840
[SPEAKER_02] emisije Franjina Ekonomija.

1841
00:56:55,840 --> 00:56:57,219
[SPEAKER_02] Tehnički urednik je danas

1842
00:56:57,219 --> 00:56:59,320
[SPEAKER_02] bio gospodin Ivan Zaradić.

1843
00:56:59,320 --> 00:57:01,139
[SPEAKER_02] Evo, neka nas gospodin blagoslovi,

1844
00:57:01,139 --> 00:57:02,019
[SPEAKER_02] neka nas čuva

1845
00:57:02,019 --> 00:57:04,400
[SPEAKER_02] i neka nas licem svojim obasija.

1846
00:57:09,079 --> 00:57:11,079
[UNKNOWN] Hvala vama.

1847
00:57:11,079 --> 00:57:13,079
[UNKNOWN] Hvala vama.

1848
